Upon this stone is written a rudimentary language.  It is difficult but you manage to read it's contents.

Here lies Kumar, Last Chieftain of the Blue Tribe.

Battled the dark men, did he.
His mighty hammer broke us free.
But in the end he could not see.
Ranger's blade his bane would will be.
[OOC: This object is used by the Job system. Check the manual on the forum if you are unsure what to do with it.]
